<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">س ق م:</span> <span class="c2">(السِّقَامُ)</span> الْمَرَضُ وَكَذَا <span class="c2">(السُّقْمُ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(السَّقَمُ)</span> مِثْلُ الْحُزْنِ وَالْحَزَنِ. وَقَدْ <span class="c2">(سَقِمَ)</span> مِنْ بَابِ طَرِبَ فَهُوَ <span class="c2">(سَقِيمٌ)</span> . وَ <span class="c2">(الْمِسْقَامُ)</span> الْكَثِيرُ السَّقَمِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>